      <title>००२ शौनकादिब्राह्मणोपदेशः</title>
      <link>https://vishvAsa.github.io/mahAbhAratam/vyAsaH/goraxapura-pAThaH/hindy-anuvAdaH/03_vanaparva/01_araNyaparva/01_vanavAsArambhaH/002_shaunakAdibrAhmaNopadeshaH/</link>
